'''Awezlan azeggaɣ''' neɣ '''Awezlan asemmaḍ''' d yiwen seg wanawen n [[itri|yitran]] meẓẓiyen, semmḍen s wassaɣ, [[Asesmel atraw|asesmel-is anitri]] seg telmest-M neɣ seg telmest-K agellal. Tuget n yitran iwezlanen [[taẓɣelt]]-nsen ddaw n 3500° C, lan [[takura]] ddaw n tkura n [[tafukt|tfukt]] (tettawaḍ ɣer 0,075 seg tkura n tfukt deg tegnit n [[Agezlan aras|iwezlanen arasen]]). 

Akken i yettwasemma daɣen s uwezlan asemmaḍ aceku taẓɣelt n tiggc-ines d tin semmḍen, ayen i yettaǧǧan ini-ines d azeggaɣ.

